## Generate Dealer Stop Motion — Deck.json Schema

Set the deck path in **Set Global Parameters -> DeckJsonPath**.
Everything else is read from Deck.json — no hardcoded values in this flow.

---

### Required sections

```json
{
  "Assets": {
    "Directory":          "D:/data/cards/MyDeck",
    "AnimationKeyframes": "D:/data/cards/MyDeck/keyframes",
    "Cut":    "D:/data/cards/MyDeck/animations/cut.mp4",
    "Fan":    "D:/data/cards/MyDeck/animations/fan.mp4",
    "Merge":  "D:/data/cards/MyDeck/animations/merge.mp4",
    "Rotate": "D:/data/cards/MyDeck/animations/rotate.mp4"
  },
  "Geometries": {
    "Animation": {
      "Width": 512, "Height": 896,
      "FrameRate": 24, "InterpolationFrames": 25
    }
  },
  "Prompts": {
    "Cut": {
      "Negative": "bad quality, blurry, distorted",
      "Keyframes": ["frame 1 positive prompt", "frame 2 positive prompt"]
    },
    "Fan":    { "Negative": "...", "Keyframes": ["...", "..."] },
    "Merge":  { "Negative": "...", "Keyframes": ["...", "..."] },
    "Rotate": { "Negative": "...", "Keyframes": ["...", "..."] }
  }
}
```

---

### Optional — safe defaults built-in

```json
{
  "Models": {
    "KeyframeCheckpoint": "dreamshaper_8.safetensors",
    "InterpolationUNet":  "wan2.2_i2v_high_noise_14B_fp8_scaled.safetensors",
    "InterpolationCLIP":  "umt5_xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors",
    "InterpolationVAE":   "wan_2.1_vae.safetensors"
  },
  "Samplers": {
    "Keyframe": {
      "Steps": 20, "CFG": 7.0, "Denoise": 1.0,
      "Sampler": "dpmpp_2m", "Scheduler": "karras"
    },
    "Interpolation": {
      "Steps": 20, "CFG": 7.0, "Denoise": 1.0, "Shift": 3.0,
      "Sampler": "uni_pc_bh2", "Scheduler": "sgm_uniform"
    }
  }
}
```

---

**AnimationTypes** (Set Global Parameters) must match the top-level keys
listed under Prompts in the deck file.  Default: `Cut,Fan,Merge,Rotate`

**To use a different model**: add the Models section to Deck.json — no
changes to the flow are required.

**To insert a hand-crafted image**: place it in the ComfyUI output
directory named exactly `KF_<AnimType>_<Index>.png` before running;
the Poll node detects it and skips generation automatically.

